        <tr> 
         <td class="oddRowEvenCol"> <h3>Welcome to the IIM Institutional Repository...</h3><p>The Faculty of Medicine, University of Colombo is the second oldest medical school in South Asia and the forerunner of university education in this country. For nearly a century it was the only medical school in the island and its contribution to the health of the nation by way of providing health services, medical education and medical research is difficult to measure. From 25 students in 1870, the student number increased to about 500 in the '60s and 1533 at present. The staff strength too has increased considerably.</p><p>Moving a step further, the Faculty now launches a comprehensive <span style="color:#7b277a;font-weight:bold;">Institutional Repository (IIM IR)</span> of its intellectual assets in digital format.The <span style="color:#7b277a;font-weight:bold;">IIM IR</span> features digital archives of theses, research reports, presentations, teaching materials, speeches, video recordings etc. Most items in our repository are freely accessible by all except for some special items with limited access due to copyright restrictions.</p><p>If you have information materials that you would like to share with your colleagues, please contact the IIM IR Team. We will be willing to incorporate them into IIM IR.</p><br><p>Thank you,</p><p>IIM IR Team</p><br> </td> 
        </tr> 
